  "What is the 'GCF method' for finding an empirical formula?": "",
  "Divide all subscripts by the greatest common factor to get the simplest ratio": "",
  "Find the GCF of atomic masses": "",
  "Multiply all subscripts by the GCF": "",
  "Add all subscripts together": "",
